parameters.name: UTCTIME3550
parameters.description: UTC at Mars when downlink ray has closest approach distance of 3550 km

parameters.name: AREOCENTRICLAT3550
parameters.description: Areocentric north latitude of closest approach point of downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: AREOCENTRICLON3550
parameters.description: Areocentric east longitude of closest approach point of downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: SZA3550
parameters.description: Solar zenith angle of closest approach point of downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: LTST3550
parameters.description: Local true solar time of closest approach point of downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: LS3550
parameters.description: Areocentric east longitude of the Sun (Ls) at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: NXFLAG
parameters.description: Occultation direction flag: 0 if ingress occultation, 1 if egress occultation

parameters.name: BSPFILENAME
parameters.description: The name of the SPK file used in processing

parameters.name: UPLINKBAND
parameters.description: The Band identifier for uplink:  X denotes X-Band.  0 indicates no uplink.

parameters.name: UPLINKANTENNA
parameters.description: Identifier for the DSN antenna used for uplink;  00  if there was no uplink

parameters.name: DOWNLINKBAND
parameters.description: The Band identifier for downlink: X denotes X-Band

parameters.name: DOWNLINKANTENNA
parameters.description: Identifier for the DSN antenna used for downlink

parameters.name: MSOX3550
parameters.description: X-coordinate in the MSO reference frame of the closest approach point of the downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: MSOY3550
parameters.description: Y-coordinate in the MSO reference frame of the closest approach point of the downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: MSOZ3550
parameters.description: Z-coordinate in the MSO reference frame of the closest approach point of the downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: MSOLAT3550
parameters.description: North latitude in the MSO reference frame of the closest approach point of the downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550

parameters.name: MSOLON3550
parameters.description: East longitude in the MSO reference frame of the closest approach point of the downlink ray at time UTCTIME3550
